document_title: Early stage (early) breast cancer: Symptoms, diagnosis and treatment
subsection_name: ung-thu-vu-giai-doan-dau.json_4_Prognosis of survival in early stage breast cancer
subsection_content: Doctor Khiem said that the prognosis of early stage breast cancer is very positive. Both stage 0 and stage I have a 5-year survival rate of 100%. The 5-year survival rate of stage II and stage III breast cancer is about 93% and 72%, respectively. When the disease metastasizes distantly, about 22% of stage IV breast cancer patients survive over the next 5 years.

ung thu vu giai doan dau.json. Prognosis of survival in early stage breast cancer
Doctor Khiem said that the prognosis of early stage breast cancer is very positive. Both stage 0 and stage I have a 5-year survival rate of 100%. The 5-year survival rate of stage II and stage III breast cancer is about 93% and 72%, respectively. When the disease metastasizes distantly, about 22% of stage IV breast cancer patients survive over the next 5 years.
